Package: swadlr
Title: Access the EPI State of Working America Data Library API
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Ben", "Zipperer", , "benzipperer@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides functions to retrieve data from the Economic Policy
    Institute's State of Working America Data Library (SWADL) API. Enables
    users to explore available indicators, measures, and dimensions, and
    to fetch time series data at national, regional, and state levels.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://benzipperer.github.io/swadlr/,
    https://github.com/benzipperer/swadlr
BugReports: https://github.com/benzipperer/swadlr/issues
Depends:
    R (>= 4.1)
Imports:
    httr2,
    jsonlite
Suggests:
    httptest2,
    knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Config/testthat/edition: 3
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
